## Installation

### Barrel

```ts
import {
  Collapsible,
  CollapsibleDefaultPanel,
  CollapsibleDefaultTrigger,
  CollapsiblePanel,
  CollapsibleTrigger,
} from "kumo-svelte";
```

### Granular

```ts
import {
  Collapsible,
  CollapsibleDefaultPanel,
  CollapsibleDefaultTrigger,
  CollapsiblePanel,
  CollapsibleTrigger,
} from "kumo-svelte/components/collapsible";
```

## Usage

Collapsible uses named Svelte components for full composition control.

### With Default Styling

Use `CollapsibleDefaultTrigger` and `CollapsibleDefaultPanel` for the classic Kumo style:

```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  import { Collapsible, CollapsibleDefaultPanel, CollapsibleDefaultTrigger } from "kumo-svelte";

  let open = $state(false);
</script>

<Collapsible bind:open>
  <CollapsibleDefaultTrigger>Show details</CollapsibleDefaultTrigger>
  <CollapsibleDefaultPanel>
    Content with border-left accent styling.
  </CollapsibleDefaultPanel>
</Collapsible>
```

### Custom Trigger

Use `CollapsibleTrigger` and `CollapsiblePanel` for full control over trigger and panel styling:

```svelte
<Collapsible bind:open>
  <CollapsibleTrigger class="rounded-md border px-3 py-1.5">
    {open ? "Hide" : "Show"} details
  </CollapsibleTrigger>
  <CollapsiblePanel class="mt-2 rounded-lg bg-kumo-tint p-4">
    Custom styled panel content.
  </CollapsiblePanel>
</Collapsible>
```

